<BaseLayout title="About | DevOps Globe"><section class="shell max-w-4xl py-16"><p class="eyebrow">About DevOps Globe</p><h1 class="mt-3 text-5xl font-black">For the people behind reliable software.</h1><p class="prose-lead mt-6">DevOps Globe exists to translate the fast-moving world of infrastructure into practical context: what changed, why it matters, and what to do next.</p><div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2"><div class="card p-6"><h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Our mission</h2><p class="mt-3 text-slate-400">Make operational knowledge generous, specific, and useful across every cloud and every team shape.</p></div><div class="card p-6"><h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Editorial skills</h2><p class="mt-3 text-slate-400">Kubernetes · SRE · IaC · Security · Observability · Cloud economics</p></div></div><h2 class="mt-14 text-3xl font-bold">Our timeline</h2><ol class="mt-6 border-l border-indigo-400 pl-6 text-slate-400"><li class="mb-6"><b class="text-white">2024 — The idea</b><br/>A calmer place for engineering signal.</li><li class="mb-6"><b class="text-white">2025 — Editorial desk</b><br/>Monthly deep dives begin.</li><li><b class="text-white">2026 — DevOps Globe</b><br/>A global conversation for modern operators.</li></ol><p class="mt-12">Say hello: <a class="text-indigo-300" href="mailto:hello@example.com">hello@example.com</a> · <a class="text-indigo-300" href="https://linkedin.com">LinkedIn</a></p></section></BaseLayout>
